            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-navy-950 mb-2">Criminal Defense</h3>
          <p class="text-navy-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">DUI, drug charges, white-collar crime, and felony defense. Aggressive representation to protect your rights and freedom.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="practice-card">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-navy-950 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-gold-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8.25 21v-4.875c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125V21m0 0h4.5V3.545M12.75 21h7.5V10.75M2.25 21h1.5m18 0h-18M2.25 9l4.5-1.636M18.75 3l-1.5.545m0 6.205 3 1m1.5.5-1.5-.5M6.75 7.364V3h-3v18m3-13.636 10.5-3.819" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-navy-950 mb-2">Real Estate Law</h3>
          <p class="text-navy-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Transactions, zoning disputes, title issues, and landlord-tenant law. Expert guidance for property matters.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center mt-12 reveal">
        <a href="/practice-areas/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-navy-950 font-semibold hover:text-gold-600 transition-colors group">
          Learn More About Our Services
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5 21 12m0 0-7.5 7.5M21 12H3" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Choose Us -->
  <section class="bg-warm-100/50 py-20 md:py-24 border-y border-navy-100/20">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="md:flex items-start gap-16">
        <div class="md:w-5/12 mb-10 md:mb-0 reveal">
          <p class="section-label text-gold-600 mb-4">Why Choose Us</p>
          <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl text-navy-950 mb-6">A Firm Built on Integrity & Results</h2>
          <p class="text-navy-500 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            At Bridger & Associates, we believe every client deserves direct access to their attorney, honest case evaluations, and aggressive advocacy. We don't take shortcuts — we prepare every case as if it's going to trial.
          </p>
          <a href="/attorneys/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-navy-950 font-semibold hover:text-gold-600 transition-colors group">
            Meet Our Attorneys
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5 21 12m0 0-7.5 7.5M21 12H3" />
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="md:w-7/12 grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-5 stagger-children">
