              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-navy-950 mb-1.5">Direct Attorney Access</h3>
            <p class="text-navy-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">You'll always speak directly with your attorney — not a paralegal or assistant.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 border border-navy-100/50">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-gold-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gold-700" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v12m-3-2.818.879.659c1.171.879 3.07.879 4.242 0 1.172-.879 1.172-2.303 0-3.182C13.536 12.219 12.768 12 12 12c-.725 0-1.45-.22-2.003-.659-1.106-.879-1.106-2.303 0-3.182s2.9-.879 4.006 0l.415.33M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-navy-950 mb-1.5">No Fee Unless We Win</h3>
            <p class="text-navy-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Personal injury cases are handled on contingency — you pay nothing unless we recover for you.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 border border-navy-100/50">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-gold-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gold-700" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v6h4.5m4.5 0a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-navy-950 mb-1.5">Responsive & Available</h3>
            <p class="text-navy-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">We return calls within 24 hours and keep you informed at every stage of your case.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 border border-navy-100/50">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-gold-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gold-700" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.26 10.147a60.438 60.438 0 0 0-.491 6.347A48.62 48.62 0 0 1 12 20.904a48.62 48.62 0 0 1 8.232-4.41 60.46 60.46 0 0 0-.491-6.347m-15.482 0a50.636 50.636 0 0 0-2.658-.813A59.906 59.906 0 0 1 12 3.493a59.903 59.903 0 0 1 10.399 5.84c-.896.248-1.783.52-2.658.814m-15.482 0A50.717 50.717 0 0 1 12 13.489a50.702 50.702 0 0 1 7.74-3.342M6.75 15a.75.75 0 1 0 0-1.5.75.75 0 0 0 0 1.5Zm0 0v-3.675A55.378 55.378 0 0 1 12 8.443m-7.007 11.55A5.981 5.981 0 0 0 6.75 15.75v-1.5" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-navy-950 mb-1.5">Trial-Ready Preparation</h3>
            <p class="text-navy-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Every case is prepared with trial-level thoroughness, giving you maximum leverage in negotiations.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Testimonials -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-14 reveal">
        <p class="section-label text-gold-600 mb-4 justify-center">Client Testimonials</p>
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl text-navy-950 mb-4">What Our Clients Say</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 stagger-children">
