            "Robert handled our commercial lease dispute with precision. His negotiation skills saved our company over $200K and avoided a costly trial. Professional, strategic, and worth every penny."
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-navy-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
